{
  "info": {
    "name": "Coffee Code API",
    "description": "Coleccion de pruebas para el API Central de Coffee Code (Mesero, Caja, Cocina). El modulo de Admin se prueba via la web Flask, no aqui.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://127.0.0.1:8010"
    },
    {
      "key": "token_mesero",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "token_cajero",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "token_cocinero",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "mesa_id",
      "value": "1"
    },
    {
      "key": "usuario_id_mesero",
      "value": "4"
    },
    {
      "key": "producto_id",
      "value": "1"
    },
    {
      "key": "pedido_id",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "ingrediente_id",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 - Login",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login Mesero",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const data_login_mesero = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('token_mesero', data_login_mesero.access_token);",
                  "pm.test('login exitoso', () => pm.response.code === 200);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"correo_electronico\": \"mesero@coffeecode.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Mesero123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Cajero",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const data_login_cajero = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('token_cajero', data_login_cajero.access_token);",
                  "pm.test('login exitoso', () => pm.response.code === 200);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"correo_electronico\": \"cajero@coffeecode.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Cajero123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Cocinero",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const data_login_cocinero = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('token_cocinero', data_login_cocinero.access_token);",
                  "pm.test('login exitoso', () => pm.response.code === 200);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"correo_electronico\": \"cocinero@coffeecode.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Cocinero123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "02 - Mesero",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar Mesas",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token_mesero}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/mesas",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "mesas"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear Pedido",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const data_crear_pedido = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (data_crear_pedido.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('pedido_id', data_crear_pedido.id); }",
                  "pm.test('pedido creado (201)', () => pm.response.code === 201);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token_mesero}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"mesa_id\": {{mesa_id}},\n  \"usuario_id\": {{usuario_id_mesero}},\n  \"items\": [\n    { \"id_producto\": {{producto_id}}, \"cantidad\": 2, \"especificaciones\": \"sin azucar\" }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/pedidos",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "pedidos"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar Pedidos (todos)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token_mesero}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/pedidos",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "pedidos"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener Pedido por ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token_mesero}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/pedidos/{{pedido_id}}",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "pedidos",
                "{{pedido_id}}"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Marcar Pedido como Entregado",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token_mesero}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json; charset=utf-8"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"estatus\": \"Entregado\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/pedidos/{{pedido_id}}/estado",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "pedidos",
                "{{pedido_id}}",
                "estado"
              ]
            },
            "description": "IMPORTANTE: si corres la coleccion completa de una sola pasada, este request fallara con 409 porque se ejecuta antes de la carpeta 03 - Cocina (el pedido aun esta en Pendiente, no en Listo). Eso es la maquina de estados rechazando una transicion invalida correctamente, no un bug. Para probarlo de verdad: corre primero 01 - Login, 02 - Mesero (menos este request), toda la carpeta 03 - Cocina, y al final vuelve a este request."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
